{"fadeType":1,"once":true,"scripts":[{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"\"At the edge of that gloomy forest, three beasts blocked my path\"","dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","bgm":"bsm-2","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"The Leopard, the Lion, and the She-Wolf.","dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"And so, I looked desperately back toward the dark forest, to such annoyance...","dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"You're back to reading those stuffy old books again? What's the story this time?","dir":1,"actorName":"Tester","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"A lost soul searching for redemption. Just another pile of clich√©d metaphors.","dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"The legendary poem of the Sardegna Empire, huh...","dir":1,"actorName":"Tester","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"The Leopard, the Lion, and the She-Wolf are just Iris Libre, the Royal Navy, and the Iron Blood.","dir":1,"actorName":"Tester","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"In the end, the Sardegnians make their way up the mountain, looking for a path to peace and redemption. But I wonder if their story truly ends as a comedy...","dir":1,"actorName":"Tester","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"...","dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Not quite...","dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"The three beasts represent the Sardegna Empire's hesitation, arrogance, and envy.","dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"The Empire fled and took a different path...","dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"In climbing the mountain, they may have gained clarity of vision, but they also lost sight of their original goal.","dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"In the end, they failed to slay their beasts.","dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"SHENSHENGDEBEIXIJU23","fadeOut":1.5}